'''科隆三王礼拜堂'''（Chapel of the Three Kings of Cologne）是英格兰[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]科尔斯顿街的一座教堂，靠近[[圣诞阶梯|圣诞阶梯]]（Christmas Steps）的顶部，已被列为 II* 级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]<ref>{{NHLE |num=1202144 |desc=Chapel of the Three Kings of Cologne |accessdate=2007-05-28}}</ref><ref name=nhle>{{NHLE|desc=Chapel of the Three Kings of Cologne|num=1202144|accessdate=23 October 2016}}</ref>。

科隆三王是指圣经中的[[東方三王|東方三王]]，模仿了[[科隆主教座堂|科隆主教座堂]]的三王小堂<ref name=he>{{cite web|title=Chapel of the Three Kings of Cologne, Colston Street, Bristol|url=https://historicengland.org.uk/services-skills/education/educational-images/chapel-of-the-three-kings-of-cologne-colston-street-379353|publisher=Historic England|access-date=23 October 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023203353/https://historicengland.org.uk/services-skills/education/educational-images/chapel-of-the-three-kings-of-cologne-colston-street-379353|archive-date=23 October 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Flaneur|first1=B.|title=The Three Kings of Cologne Chapel, The John Foster Almshouse, Bristol|url=https://anticsroadshowblogspot.wordpress.com/2014/11/21/the-three-kings-of-cologne-chapel-john-fosters-almshouse-bristol-210814/|publisher=The Antics Roadshow blog|access-date=23 October 2016|archive-date=2016-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220090747/https://anticsroadshowblogspot.wordpress.com/2014/11/21/the-three-kings-of-cologne-chapel-john-fosters-almshouse-bristol-210814/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中一扇窗户描绘了 [[耶稣诞生|耶稣诞生]]场景，这可能就是圣诞阶梯名称的由来。<ref>{{cite web|title=Christmas Steps: Ghosts, myths and fish 'n' chips|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/bristol/content/articles/2004/07/12/christmas_steps_feature.shtml|publisher=BBC|access-date=23 October 2016|archive-date=2020-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516001506/http://www.bbc.co.uk/bristol/content/articles/2004/07/12/christmas_steps_feature.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Christmas Steps How did iconic street get its festive name?|url=http://www.bristolpost.co.uk/christmas-steps-did-iconic-street-festive/story-25753884-detail/story.html|access-date=23 October 2016|work=Bristol Post|date=23 December 2014}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

教堂是由约翰·福斯特建于1504年。他是该市的警长、市长和议员。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Mountney|first1=Hugh|title=The Three Holy Kings of Cologne: How They Journeyed from Persia to Cologne and Their Veneration in England|date=2003|publisher=Gracewing|isbn=9780852444078|page=7|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Z7UsrIcUfs8C&q=Chapel+of+the+Three+Kings+of+Cologne+Bristol&pg=PA7}}</ref> 该堂是毗邻的[[福斯特济贫院|福斯特济贫院]]（Foster's Almshouses）的礼拜堂<ref name="Brace">{{cite book |last=Brace |first=Keith |title=Portrait of Bristol |year=1976 |publisher=Robert Hale |location=London |isbn=0-7091-5435-6 }}</ref>。济贫院院长负责维持教堂，任命牧师。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Ross|first1=Charles Derek|title=Cartulary of St. Mark's Hospital, Bristol, Volume 21|date=1959|publisher=Bristol Record Society|pages=287–288|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rD0SAAAAIAAJ&q=Chapel+of+the+Three+Kings+of+Cologne+Bristol&pg=PA287|access-date=2016-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023210539/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=rD0SAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA287&lpg=PA287&dq=Chapel+of+the+Three+Kings+of+Cologne+Bristol&source=bl&ots=NB2b4fjJKK&sig=609gv0HWlD-lcXBaE-Mgsjq8uPw&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjFuJCd4PDPAhVFBcAKHU9jDJc4ChDoAQg4MAY#v=onepage&q=Chapel%20of%20the%20Three%20Kings%20of%20Cologne%20Bristol&f=false|archive-date=2016-10-23}}</ref>

1861年，福斯特和伍德重新粉刷修理屋顶，1865年进一步修复，其中包括用于安装雕刻的壁龛。<ref name=he/><ref name="Brace"/> 目前的三座雕像由欧内斯特·帕斯科设计，安装于20世纪60年代。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Foyle|first1=Andrew|title=Bristol (Pevsner Architectural Guides: City Guides)|date=2004|publisher=Yale University Press|isbn=978-0300104424|page=[https://archive.org/details/bristol0000foyl/page/132 132]|url=https://archive.org/details/bristol0000foyl/page/132}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Beyond The Walls Three Kings of Cologne|url=https://www.about-bristol.co.uk/out-03.asp|publisher=About Bristol|access-date=23 October 2016|archive-date=2001-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010725053237/http://www.about-bristol.co.uk/out-03.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在雕像上方的[[山墙|山墙]]上是一口小钟<ref name=nhle/>。

截至2007年，毗邻的[[福斯特济贫院|福斯特济贫院]]已改建为私人住宅，教堂可供居民使用。

